title: School Boy Q Interview and more
itunes:title: School Boy Q Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had School Boy Q stop by where he spoke about his new album, not censoring around his daughter and more. Also, after new broke about Bun B saving his queen from an intruder, Charlamagne gave the "Donkey of the Day" to the man that dared to test Bun B's gangsta and for him to appreciate his blessing. Moreover, Angela also helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" especially with one listener that needed help about hygiene.
